raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.9.19" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-luminescence
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Luminescence_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/Luminescence/Luminescence_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 19b54c3c5c642ec9f583b2b1af4c39a33d5940c14f5135c004c26fbb69d342c3

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  skip: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-deoptim >=2.2_6
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.7
    - r-rcpparmadillo >=0.10.6.0.0
    - r-xml >=3.99
    - r-bbmle >=1.0.24
    - r-data.table >=1.14.0
    - r-httr >=1.4.2
    - r-lamw >=2.1.0
    - r-matrixstats >=0.60.0
    - r-mclust >=5.4.7
    - r-minpack.lm >=1.2_1
    - r-plotrix >=3.8_1
    - r-raster >=3.4_10
    - r-readxl >=1.3.1
    - r-shape >=1.4.6
    - r-zoo >=1.8
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-deoptim >=2.2_6
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.7
    - r-rcpparmadillo >=0.10.6.0.0
    - r-xml >=3.99
    - r-bbmle >=1.0.24
    - r-data.table >=1.14.0
    - r-httr >=1.4.2
    - r-lamw >=2.1.0
    - r-matrixstats >=0.60.0
    - r-mclust >=5.4.7
    - r-minpack.lm >=1.2_1
    - r-plotrix >=3.8_1
    - r-raster >=3.4_10
    - r-readxl >=1.3.1
    - r-shape >=1.4.6
    - r-zoo >=1.8

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('Luminescence')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('Luminescence')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=Luminescence
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: A collection of various R functions for the purpose of Luminescence dating data analysis. This includes, amongst others, data import, export, application of age models, curve deconvolution, sequence analysis and plotting of equivalent dose distributions.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
